  Locus:
    Page: 476
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Truth
---
Everything that is true is beautiful. Theonly vanity under the sun is error
andfalsehood. Even pain and death arebeautiful because they are the
workwhich purifies and the transfigurationwhich delivers.
